posting_body: ['6 Lincoln Street managed by Cornerstone Apartments', 'Bedrooms:', '1', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Square Ft.:', '540', 'Price:', '$1564/mo.', 'Welcome to the Abraham!', 'A building with a wide array of amentities, including reserved parking, on-site laundry, and much more.', "If you're looking for a quinntesential Denver area, look no further, The Abraham has multiple close parks including Dailey Park, Hungarian Freedom Park, and a Alamo Placita Park.", 'All good recreational spots in the city for anyone to walk their dog, spend some lounge time, or just enjoy the denver air.', 'Come schedule your tour today!', 'Features:', 'On-Site Laundry', 'Recycling', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Dishwasher', 'Controlled Access', 'Balconies', 'In-Unit Laundry', 'Reserved Parking', 'Contact us:', 'To schedule a showing please contact our leasing team at', 'To apply NOW please visit <URL>', 'Nearby Neighborhoods:', "Five Points, University of Denver, Cheesman Park, West Wash Park, Highlands, Uptown, Sloan's Lake, Downtown, Hale, Capitol Hill, Jefferson Park, Platt Park, RiNo, Congress Park, Baker, City Park, LoHi", 'Availability and pricing are subject to change.']
